WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.507
Internally, our strict policy is to utilize this purchasing route

00:00:04.507 --> 00:00:09.014
only when it guarantees a distinct, measurable sales edge. We

00:00:09.014 --> 00:00:13.521
typically reserve this powerful motion for strategic opportunities valued over

00:00:13.521 --> 00:00:18.027
one hundred thousand dollars, requiring a solid, well-documented business case

00:00:18.027 --> 00:00:22.534
for internal approval. Precision Point: While AppsFlyer pays listing fees

00:00:22.534 --> 00:00:27.041
to AWS for facilitating these transactions, these strategic fees are

00:00:27.041 --> 00:00:31.548
absorbed at the corporate level and do not negatively affect

00:00:31.548 --> 00:00:36.055
your personal opportunity revenue calculations or quota retirement.
